            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "No, we don't have that package here."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, I see. I wonder if it got stopped somewhere..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x4,
            "voice_id": 0x21f,
            "name_id": 0x39,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "unknown2": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "It's hard to say. I'll let you know when we find out anything. I've got to get going now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Okay. Thank you."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0xf5,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Oh, goodness gracious. Working with an unfamiliar supplier is hard at a time like this..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Did you not get a package delivery?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0xf7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Yup. I couldn't get in touch with the caravan I always use..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "So I was gonna have it delivered via several different points, but..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "It went missing at some point.<CR>Urgh, I shouldn't have done<CR>something I wasn't used to."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "I guess not getting items is a matter of life and death for a store..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15d,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "And deliveries getting delayed have been happening more frequently these days. Ugh, it's so much trouble."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x15f,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "I guess I have to go to each transit point and... Wait, maybe I should go to the original supplier..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Oh, I don't want to get in the way of your work, so I'll just be going..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Hold on! ...Ayeshaaaa, you're looking very cute today."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Wh-What's with the sudden change?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x69,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Ohhh, Ayesha, you look like you really wanna go to Hornheim."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Huh? Oh, I see, so that's what it is."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0xa,
            "name_id": 0xa,
            "extra_id": 0x6d,
            "expr_id": 0x2,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Sorry. I just want you to go ask the supplier about the situation."
